WHAT IS THIS FILE
The certified optical DNA profile for the Nikon NIKKOR Z 50mm f/1.2 S-Line
lens. It covers the Nano Crystal Coat gradient-index effect, ARNEO coat,
SR (Short-wavelength Refractive) glass, and the Z-mount geometry that
reduces vignetting.

WHY IT EXISTS
Nikon's S-Line lenses exploit the 55 mm inner diameter and 16 mm flange
focal distance of the Z-mount to place large rear elements close to the
sensor. This file mathematically captures those design advantages, enabling
correct virtual production and VFX integration for Nikon-shot content.

HOW IT WORKS
1. Optical construction: 17 elements in 14 groups, including 2 ED glass
   elements, 1 aspherical element, and elements with Nano Crystal Coat.

2. Nano Crystal Coat:
   Gradient-index layer: a nano-particle structure creates a gradual transition
   of refractive index from air to glass, δn → 0 at boundary.
   Reflectance < 0.1% over 380–780 nm range.
   Effective for incident angles 0°–60°.

3. ARNEO coat:
   Multi-layer anti-reflective coating optimized for near-vertical incident
   light. Complements Nano Crystal Coat by suppressing reflections that the
   gradient layer misses. Combined, the two coatings yield reflectance
   < 0.05% over 450–680 nm.

4. SR glass element:
   Short-wavelength Refractive glass with unusually high refractive index for
   blue/violet light (n_blue > n_green significantly). This corrects the
   secondary spectrum, eliminating purple fringing in high-contrast edges.

5. Z-mount geometry:
   Inner diameter: 55 mm
   Flange focal distance: 16 mm
   This large throat and short flange allow the rear element to sit very close
   to the sensor. Result: chief ray angle at sensor corners < 12°, minimizing
   vignetting and color shading.
   Measured corner illumination at f/1.2: 62% (≈0.7 EV fall-off).

6. Distortion:
     k1 = -0.0042, k2 = 0.0009, k3 = 0.0000
     p1 = p2 ≈ 0
   Near-zero distortion (<0.3%).

7. Bokeh characteristics:
   9-blade rounded diaphragm. Spherical aberration deliberately under-corrected
   at f/1.2 for soft, smooth background blur. No onion-ring texture due to
   precision aspherical polishing.

